# Bundle Builder Architecture

EcomExperts take-home. Full context: `AGENTS.md` at repo root.

## Repo

- `client/` — React + TS + Tailwind
- `server/` — Express + TS + SQLite (**no JSON Server mock**)

## Phase

FE first via `api/client.ts` + `local.ts`. BE later — flip `VITE_USE_API=true`. Will not break FE if contract holds.

## Rules

- Components **never** import `bundle.json` — only `api.*`
- Catalog read-only; selections in reducer; totals derived
- localStorage required for "Save my system for later"
- Optimistic UI + debounced PATCH when API enabled
- Server authoritative at quote/checkout; never trust client prices

## Variant qty (critical)

Separate qty per `productId:variantId`. Card stepper = active variant. Review shows all variants with qty > 0.

## Product requires

Catalog `requires: string[]` on products; auto-add/remove companions in `selections`. Lock state derived — mirror on server PATCH.

## API (fixed)

`GET /api/v1/config` · `POST/PATCH/GET /api/v1/configurations/:id` · `POST .../save` · `POST .../quote` · `POST .../checkout`

## Figma

Desktop `1:342` · Tablet `1:27` · Mobile `1:658`
